://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-email.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-printer.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111226-hongkong-china-136220953.html#comments\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-comments.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.google.com/buzz/post?message=%E5%88%98%E6%99%93%E6%B3%A2%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%952%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4+%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%AF%E8%81%94%E4%BC%9A%E5%9C%A3%E8%AF%9E%E6%B8%B8%E8%A1%8C%E4%BF%83%E9%87%8A%E6%94%BE&#038;url=http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111226-hongkong-china-136220953.html\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-googleBuzz.png\" /></a></li>\n<li>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\"></a></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://twitthis.com/twit?url=http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111226-hongkong-china-136220953.html&#038;title=%E5%88%98%E6%99%93%E6%B3%A2%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%952%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4+%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%AF%E8%81%94%E4%BC%9A%E5%9C%A3%E8%AF%9E%E6%B8%B8%E8%A1%8C%E4%BF%83%E9%87%8A%E6%94%BE\"></a></li>\n<li>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p>香港市民支援民主爱国运动联合会(支联会)圣诞节举行游行，呼吁释放刘晓波和其他在押的维权人士。</p>\n<p>当地时间圣诞节中午，香港支联会二十多名成员由西区警署游行到中联办，要求北京释放刘晓波和其他所有良心犯。他们还要求停止软禁刘晓波的妻子刘霞。请愿人士将请愿信贴在中联办的铁闸门外之后离去。</p>\n<p>12月25日是一年一度的圣诞节，也是刘晓波被拘两周年。 2009年，刘晓波被当局以“颠覆国家罪”判刑十一年。2010年，刘晓波获得诺贝尔和平奖。</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<h4>相关文章</h4>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111209-China-Free-Liu-Xiaobo-135318623.html\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"90\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/images/90*90/AP090625148763.jpgLiuXiabo.jpg\" width=\"90\" /></a><br />\n<h3><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111209-China-Free-Liu-Xiaobo-135318623.html\">诺奖得主人权团体再促释放刘晓波</a> <img align=\"top\" border=\"0\" height=\"10\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-media-watch.gif\" width=\"10\" /><img align=\"top\" border=\"0\" height=\"10\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-media-comment-gray.gif\" width=\"12\" /></h3>\n<p>国际特赦等人权团体和五名诺奖得主近日呼吁中国当局释放仍被监禁的诺贝尔和平奖得主刘晓波以及其他人权活动人士。另一方面，中国政府表示，刘晓波触犯法律，理应坐牢。北京分析人士认为，刘晓波获释前景不容乐观。</p>\n<div>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/china/20111209-CHINA-RIGHTS-135308153.html\">中国坚持关押诺奖得主刘晓波</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-email.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-printer.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111226-hongkong-china-136220953.html#comments\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-comments.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.google.com/buzz/post?message=%E5%88%98%E6%99%93%E6%B3%A2%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%952%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4+%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%AF%E8%81%94%E4%BC%9A%E5%9C%A3%E8%AF%9E%E6%B8%B8%E8%A1%8C%E4%BF%83%E9%87%8A%E6%94%BE&#038;url=http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111226-hongkong-china-136220953.html\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-goo